$interpreted: Left Guard: Who's there!?
Jahan: Working hard, boys? Or hardly working? HAHAHA! Oh, sorry. The Captain told me to come see how you all are holding up.
Right Guard: Hey, what a sweet little baby.
Left Guard: We got the drinks, now get the hell out of here!
Jahan: Hee...hee...hee.
Jahan: .........NOW!
Right Guard: Snickerboppers! It's a trap!
Joan: Ahhh!!!
Rune: Joan, are you okay?
Joan: (With no concern for his own safety, he rushes to save me. Alas! Could I have not one suitor, but two!?)
Joan: (...ah, what a shame. I don't like guys with giant muscles. I've made him fall for me. What kind of woman am I?)
Sophie: Why are you willing to help us?
Jahan: Jahan has had enough of them bossing him around. Hmph! When I find some dirt on Devious, I'll blackmail him for ownership of the casino!
Sophie: This room looks pretty normal...
Clark: Is there some kind of secret switch?
Clark: I don't see Joan's master.
Rune: Elio...is also not here.
Sophie: Elio, where on earth are you...?
Rune: You...LIAR!
Jahan: Me, a liar? No, no, no. I just told you I wanted to blackmail Devious.
Security Captain: Jahan, a traitor. What a surprise...*snickers*...
Rune: Everybody...be careful.
Jahan: *singing*...Jahan comes to save the day!! A shining star is headed your—
Jahan: Wait a second. Captain! I've been courageously waiting. They forced me to do this and threatened my life. Luckily, you've arrived just in time.
Sophie: Hey! You wanted to take us here!
Jahan: Don't try to frame me. Why would I involve myself in your criminal activities?
Security Captain: Get out of here! After I deal with the intruders, I'm coming for you!
Joan: Let's see here...
Joan: Hmm...up there it says...
Joan: "Gambling Competition! First Prize: Legendary, Exotic Delicacy" What!? It's already begun!? My master is going to be eaten alive!
Sophie: Let's save him first and come back for the room later!
Clark: Sophie, you truly are a good person.
Sophie: What'd you say? A good person?
Clark: Eh? My meaning was merely——
Sophie: I'm not like my father!! If you don't know what you're talking about then shut up!
Clark: ...Did I just get a scolding?
Rune: Sophie...is sad.
Clark: More like angry.
Clark: Is it not cool to be a good person these days? What am I missing?
